Text To What is a python program that is meant to function as a simple Text Alternator.
It is constructed using Tkinter and it's serves as an exercise.

Swapping caps on and off and letters with specific characters using a random number generator

The User is supposed to type the input into a window and press enter or click a button to run

After the output is printed and two buttons appear; one to copy the text and one to save it in a text file

Step by step guide of creation

1. Create window and accept input text

2. Limit acceptable characters

3. Alter text according to rules

4. Print output

5. Create Copy and Save to Text buttons

6. Refine.